"A couple of weeks ago, I went to do some work in a college. Like most colleges nowadays, many of the classrooms have data projectors, and to protect these pieces of kit they are screwed to the ceiling. This is fine but it makes them tricky to turn on, especially when you are only 5’ 3”. I did raise this with my senior manager and she suggested I stand on a table. My response is not helpfully reproduced verbatim, suffice to say that I do not stand on tables. I don't trust them to take my weight for a start."
